                <note rend="inline" type="source">793.94/1904: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Consul General at Nanking</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Peck</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1931-09-28T18:00:00-05:00"
                            >September 28, 1931—6 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>80. Please deliver to Minister for Foreign Affairs as from me the following
                    message: <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>“Reports of attack on you have shocked me and I hasten to express my
                            earnest hope for your speedy recovery.”</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Stimson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
